videos.headline: Hurts finds Lamb for OU TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts completes a touchdown pass to CeeDee Lamb on fourth-and-goal at the 1-yard line.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts finds Lamb for OU TD) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Flea-flicker leads to 51-yard TD for OU's Lamb
videos.description: CeeDee Lamb hauls in a pass from Jalen Hurts and shakes the Texas defenders to score a 51-yard touchdown on a flea-flicker.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Flea-flicker leads to 51-yard TD for OU’s Lamb) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurts goes behind-the-back to escape sack
videos.description: Jalen Hurts passes the ball behind his back and steps out of a sack to complete a pass to CeeDee Lamb.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurts goes behind-the-back to escape sack) 2019/10/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: QB-turned-RB Johnson evens the score for Texas
videos.description: Texas QB-turned-RB Roschon Johnson gets loose for a 57-yard run, then finishes the job with a four-yard touchdown to even the score at 10-10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (QB-turned-RB Johnson evens the score for Texas) 2019/10/12 ESHEET
